The tracking number assigned is 9205590153708406256252. You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you did not receive the card, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request that we resend the card to you. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Case Was Denied
body: On June 24, 2021, we denied your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190112983. We sent you a denial notice that explains why we denied your case and your options. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you do not receive your denial notice by July 9, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request a copy of the notice. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Card Was Delivered To Me By The Post Office
body: On April 12, 2021, the Post Office delivered your new card for Receipt Number YSC2190112984, to the address that you gave us. The tracking number assigned is 9205590153708405192162. You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Case Was Rejected Because It Was Improperly Filed
body: On March 23, 2021, we rejected your Form I-601A, Application for Provisional Unlawful Presence Waiver, Receipt Number YSC2190112985, because it was not filed correctly. We mailed your case back to you, including any supporting materials and fee. Please follow the instructions to resubmit your case. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Case Was Updated To Show Fingerprints Were Taken
body: As of April 29, 2021, fingerprints relating to your Form I-751, Petition to Remove Conditions on Residence, Receipt Number YSC2190112986, have been applied to your case. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
